name: PANIC ATTACK 4. DOOMSDAY BOSS FIGHT
description:
4 unique pieces of "PANIC ATTACK", the most recent Pussy Riot's activist audio-visual artwork. The VERY first Pussy Riot's NFT drop.

Pussy Riot's art was named by The Guardian among the best art pieces of the 21st century, "Women of the year" (2012) by TIME.

"DOOMSDAY BOSS FIGHT " is Judgment day. It turns out that this final boss fight is a fight of a hu(wo)man with herself, she is the one responsible for the apocalypse.
